    {
      "content": "Overview",
      "pos": [
        573,
        581
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The primary function of StorSimple Snapshot Manager is to allow you to create application-consistent backup copies of Azure StorSimple volumes in the form of snapshots.",
      "pos": [
        583,
        751
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Snapshots are then listed in an XML file called a <bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>backup catalog<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        752,
        819
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The backup catalog organizes snapshots by volume group, and then by local snapshot or cloud snapshot.",
      "pos": [
        820,
        921
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        924,
        1056
      ],
      "content": "You can view the backup catalog by expanding the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Backup Catalog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> node in the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Scope<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> pane, and then expanding the volume group."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1060,
        1204
      ],
      "content": "If you click the volume group name, the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Results<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> pane shows the number of local snapshots and cloud snapshots available for the volume group."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1209,
        1382
      ],
      "content": "If you click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Local Snapshot<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Cloud Snapshot<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Results<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> pane shows the following information about each backup snapshot (depending on your <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>View<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept> settings):"
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1391,
        1434
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Name<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – the time the snapshot was taken."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1443,
        1507
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Type<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – whether this is a local snapshot or a cloud snapshot."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        1516,
        1546
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Owner<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – the content owner."
